axis2.name: #{Changes}
axis2.text:
CASE 
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD" IN (<%=ChangedFields%>) ) > 0 
        THEN 'With Change' 
    ELSE 'Without Change' 
END

axis2.name: #{Rework}
axis2.text:
CASE 
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=rework_activities%>) ) > 0 
    THEN
        'With Rework' 
    ELSE
        'Without Rework' 
END

formula.text:
CASE
  WHEN  ISNULL(ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR"))  , 0.8, 0.15)) = 1
  THEN 'Vendor with no oder'

  WHEN ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR"))  , 0.8, 0.15) = 1
  THEN 'A'

  WHEN ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR"))  , 0.8, 0.15) = 2
  THEN 'B'

  ELSE 'C'
END

variables.name: pieChartTitle
variables.value: Aspects for a Perfect Purchase Order Item

variables.name: ButtonDrilldown2
variables.value:
CASE


WHEN
    -- No Changes 
    PU_COUNT("EKPO","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGED_FIELD" IN (<%= changed_fields %>)) = 0
AND
     -- No manual Activities
     PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>", 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" NOT IN (<%= activities_white_listed_in_automation_rate %>) AND
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" NOT IN (<%= auto_user_type %>) ) = 0 
AND
     -- No Rework on Case Level  Activities
     (PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>")
        -
     PU_COUNT_DISTINCT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" ) ) = 0
    THEN
        'Perfect Activities'
        
WHEN
 
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN ( <%= purchasing %> ) 
    THEN
        'Purchasing Department'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%= management %>) 
    THEN
        'Management'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%= logistic %>) 
    THEN
        'Logistic Department'
        
WHEN
     "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN ( <%= accounting %>) 
    THEN
        'Accounting Department'
        
    ELSE
        'Other'
END
